docs.abstract: Microsoft’s latest operating system may seem like a leap from Windows XP and Windows 7, but you can make the Windows 10 desktop feel more like home.
docs.snippet: Microsoft’s latest operating system may seem like a leap from Windows XP and Windows 7, but you can make the Windows 10 desktop feel more like home.
docs.lead_paragraph: Q. I want to make Windows 10 appear more like earlier versions of Windows. Is it possible to put an icon for My Computer on my desktop?

docs.abstract: A report published by European officials said that only 40 percent of online material flagged as offensive was reviewed within 24 hours.
docs.snippet: A report published by European officials said that only 40 percent of online material flagged as offensive was reviewed within 24 hours.
docs.lead_paragraph: European officials pushed on Tuesday for American technology giants to do more to tackle online hate speech across the region, adding to the chorus of policy makers worldwide demanding greater action from the likes of Facebook, Google and Twitter.

headline.main: Europe Presses American Tech Companies to Tackle Hate Speech
headline.print_headline: Europe Presses U.S. Tech Giants to Curb Online Hate Speech

docs.abstract: One sign of success in the $26 billion merger will be if few LinkedIn employees use their own product to find another job.
docs.snippet: One sign of success in the $26 billion merger will be if few LinkedIn employees use their own product to find another job.
docs.lead_paragraph: LinkedIn is a site where workers memorialize their professional lives and look for new careers. Now, after its recent purchase by Microsoft for $26.2 billion, one good measure of the merger’s success may be how few LinkedIn employees start using their own product.

headline.main: Daily Report: What Microsoft Needs From LinkedIn
